flowchart TD
  START([evaluate / consume]) --> SUBJ{subject present?}
  SUBJ -->|no| VERR[throw RateLimitValidationError]
  SUBJ -->|yes| RESOLVE[resolve policy\nexplicit policyId OR highest-priority by subjectType]
  RESOLVE -->|none| NF[throw PolicyNotFoundError]
  RESOLVE --> INT{policy checksum valid?}
  INT -->|no| IErr[record integrityFailure\nthrow IntegrityError]
  INT -->|yes| READ[read counter state\nusage cache → provider on miss]

  READ --> ALGO{algorithm}
  ALGO -->|fixed_window| FW[count in aligned window]
  ALGO -->|sliding_window| SW[sum log within window]
  ALGO -->|token_bucket| TB[refill tokens by elapsed·rate]
  ALGO -->|leaky_bucket| LB[leak level by elapsed·rate]

  FW --> DECIDE
  SW --> DECIDE
  TB --> DECIDE
  LB --> DECIDE
  DECIDE{usage + cost <= capacity?}

  DECIDE -->|dry-run evaluate| EXPLAIN[return explanation\nallowed · remaining · resetTime\nNO mutation · RateLimitEvaluated]

  DECIDE -->|consume · allowed| WCONS[persist stateIfConsumed\nrecord allowed + consumption\nQuotaConsumed]
  DECIDE -->|consume · blocked| WDECAY[persist stateDecayed\nrecord blocked\nQuotaExceeded]

  WCONS --> RESULT([result: allowed · remaining · usage · resetTime])
  WDECAY --> RESULT
  EXPLAIN --> RESULT
